title: TomatoDialogue0
---
Tomato: Oh, hey there! I'm just a humble tomato.
Player: Hey! I am loo..
Tomato: I have some juicy secrets to share, Did you know that tomatoes are actually fruits?
Player: Actually I did...
Tomato: Yeah, it's true! We may be used in savory dishes.
Tomato: But botanically speaking, we're classified as fruits because we develop from the ovary of a flower and contain seeds.
